---
title: "Sequence Diagram: /create-docs Skill"
---
%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Claude
    participant FS as File System
    participant Glob as Glob Tool

    User->>Claude: /create-docs [type] [name] [description]

    alt No type provided
        Claude->>User: What to create?<br/>[1] rule     — scoped convention for a path<br/>[2] skill    — slash command workflow<br/>[3] agent    — subagent with tools + model<br/>[4] settings — permissions + hooks<br/>[5] claude-md — root project overview
        User->>Claude: number or type name [name]
    end

    note over Claude,Glob: Detect project stack
    Claude->>Glob: Scan root for marker files<br/>(*.sln, go.mod, Cargo.toml,<br/>package.json, pyproject.toml)
    Glob-->>Claude: Matched markers
    Claude->>FS: Read formatter/linter configs
    FS-->>Claude: Format + lint settings
    Claude->>Glob: Check for CI configs
    Glob-->>Claude: CI pipeline info
    Claude->>Claude: Resolve stack: language +<br/>framework + commands

    note over Claude,FS: Read references
    Claude->>FS: Read how-to-create-docs.md
    FS-->>Claude: Structure, frontmatter, examples
    Claude->>FS: Read markdown-style.md
    FS-->>Claude: Formatting conventions

    note over Claude,Glob: Gather context
    alt type = rule
        Claude->>Glob: Verify paths: globs match files
        Glob-->>Claude: Matched files list
    else type = skill
        opt No description in $ARGUMENTS
            Claude->>User: What should the skill do?<br/>(one sentence describing trigger + outcome)
            User->>Claude: Description
        end
    else type = agent
        Claude->>User: Choose tools and model:<br/>Tools:  [1] Read,Grep,Glob (read-only)<br/>        [2] Read,Grep,Glob,Bash<br/>        [3] All tools<br/>        [4] Custom list<br/>Model:  [A] sonnet (default)  [B] opus  [C] haiku
        User->>Claude: tools + model choice
    else type = settings
        Claude->>FS: Check settings.json exists?
        FS-->>Claude: Existing or not found
    else type = claude-md
        Claude->>FS: Check CLAUDE.md exists?
        FS-->>Claude: Existing or not found
        Claude->>FS: Read project root structure
        FS-->>Claude: Directory tree
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Generate file
    Claude->>Claude: Build content:<br/>kebab-case frontmatter,<br/>stack-specific globs/commands
    alt type = rule
        Claude->>FS: Write rules/name.md
    else type = skill
        Claude->>FS: Write skills/name/SKILL.md
    else type = agent
        Claude->>FS: Write agents/name.md
    else type = settings
        Claude->>FS: Write/merge settings.json
    else type = claude-md
        Claude->>FS: Write CLAUDE.md
    end

    note over Claude,Glob: Verify
    Claude->>FS: Check file at correct path
    FS-->>Claude: OK

    opt type = rule with paths:
        Claude->>Glob: Confirm globs match files
        Glob-->>Claude: Match count > 0
    end

    opt type = skill
        Claude->>FS: Confirm supporting files exist
        FS-->>Claude: OK
    end

    opt type = claude-md
        Claude->>Claude: Confirm no remaining placeholders
    end

    Claude->>User: [CREATED] .claude/path — summary<br/>[STACK] Detected: language + framework
